			<div class="snippet">
				<p>
	For LafargeHolcim, being a leader in the building materials industry means having the resources necessary to pursue the best return on capital for our shareholders and investors.</p>
			</div>

			<div class="readmore">
											<a href="https://www.lafargeholcim.com/investor-relations">Learn more</a>
